Handle Numeric Values

CRM Analytics internally stores numeric values as long values. The maximum value is 36,028,797,018,963,967 and the minimum value is -36,028,797,018,963,968.
Confirm that numeric values in a column are uniform in granularity and units.
When creating or updating a dataset, CRM Analytics replaces blank numeric values with the specified default value. If no default value is specified, CRM Analytics replaces blanks with 0 or null based on whether you enable null measure handling.
